headline: Chase Bank to continue its move into Rochester with plans for a second branch
summary: Oct. 18—ROCHESTER — Before starting construction of its first branch in Rochester, JPMorgan Chase Bank is moving forward with plans for a second one. Earlier this year, Chase Bank announced its introduction into the Rochester market with plans for a 3,421-square-foot branch on the corner of Apache Drive Southwest and 12th Street Southwest in front of the Apache Mall.
